<emphasis bold="true" box="[623,810,1446,1473]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="63">Pseudocanthon</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bates, H. W." box="[818,960,1446,1473]" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" refId="ref18875" refString="Bates, H. W. (1887) Tribe Lamellicornia. In: Bates, H. W. (1886 - 1889) Biologia Centrali-Americana. Insecta. Coleoptera. Volume II. Part 2. Pectinicornia and Lamellicornia. Taylor and Francis, London, United Kingdom, pp. 25 - 64, pls. 2 - 3. [publication date following Bousquet (2016)]" type="journal volume" year="1887">Bates, 1887</bibRefCitation>
